Class ASCIICharProp

java.lang.Object
  org.opends.sdk.util.ASCIICharProp
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<ASCIICharProp>
public final class ASCIICharProp
extends Object
implements Comparable<ASCIICharProp>

A ASCIICharProp provides fast access to ASCII character properties. In particular, the ability to query whether or not a character is a letter, a digit, hexadecimal character, as well as various methods for performing character conversions.

The methods in this class do not perform memory allocations nor calculations and so can be used safely in high performance situations.
